    <p>Mercedes-Benz has l aunched the Mercedes Me Con­nect e-concierge ser­vice here.</p>
    <p>The down­load­able app helps own­ers find their Mercs in a sprawl­ing carpark, check their ve­hi­cle’s sta­tus, book a ser­vic­ing slot and sum­mon for ac­ci­dent re­cov­ery.</p>
    <p>It can also link to the owner’s Google Home and fit­ness wear­ables, and of­fer real-life traf­fic in­for­ma­tion with In­ter­net-of-every­thing con­nec­tiv­ity.</p>


